modName: Map Overhaul BAIN Conversion File - BCF
descriptionHtml:
This is a BAIN Conversion File - BCF for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=4991]Map Overhaul[/url] this requires the Map Overhaul - v2-0-4, Map Texture and Mesh Pack, Follower Map Markers, Remove 3D Map Camera Limits, and Necessary Map Markers archives.

Thanks to [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/modules/members/index.php?id=3106025]xAtomz[/url] for permission and the original mod.
